[V1]
 Sacred, holy, pure,
 Lord of space and time,
 Dwells in perfect light,
 Radiance sublime.
 Sacred holy songs
 Rise on wings of praise;
 All creation rings
 With echoes of Your grace.
 
[C]
 And oh, my grateful heart rejoices at Your name.
 And oh, my grateful heart rejoices at Your name.
 
[V2]
 Sacred, risen Son,
 Peerless Lamb of God;
 Mercy, grace and peace
 Rolling like a flood.
 Promise forged in pain,
 Forgiveness bought by blood;
 Sealed with sacred words
 From the mouth of God.
 
